      "raw_text": "While passing the city hall the IL\ncaravan wagons of the Forbes Team\nIng company and the Sprague Warner\ncompany were assaulted by missiles\n\n\nand eggs tlled with acid. The negro\ndrivers drew black jacks and revolv-\ners. but before they could fire all\nwere arrested. The arrested men are\nImported strike breakers and arrived\nthis morning. The president of the\nChicago Federation of Labor called\nmeeting today of the joint strike"
